// ==================== API ENDPOINT SUMMARY ====================
/*
 POST  /api/v1/auth/register          → register new user
 POST  /api/v1/auth/login             → login & get JWT

 POST  /api/v1/medications            → log medication intake
 GET   /api/v1/medications            → list all medication entries

 POST  /api/v1/symptoms               → log symptom with severity
 GET   /api/v1/symptoms               → list all symptoms

 POST  /api/v1/vitals                 → log vitals (BP, weight, HR, etc.)
 GET   /api/v1/vitals?days=7          → vitals for past N days

 POST  /api/v1/moods                  → log daily mood
 GET   /api/v1/moods                  → list mood entries

 POST  /api/v1/journal                → create journal entry
 GET   /api/v1/journal                → list journal entries
 GET   /api/v1/journal/shared         → entries shared with doctor

 GET   /api/v1/summary                → full health summary report
*/
